   tourism destinations. Enhanced information access coupled with a new
   kind of tourists avid for online content and predisposed to share
   information on social media, allows for a better understanding of
   tourist behaviour regarding their spatial distribution in urban
   destinations. Thus, smart tourism portrays individuals as information
