Abstract = {{Although smart-card data secures collective travel information on public
   transportation users, the reality is that only a few cities are equipped
   with an automatic fare collection (AFC) system that can provide user
   information for both boarding and alighting locations. Many researchers
   have delved into forecasting the destinations of smart-card users. Such
