   the city. This analysis is to showcase the green index for the planning
   of smart cities. The devised green index is verified in the real-world
   context of Gulbarga city, India, thereby understanding the practicality
   of this index. The results show scope for alternative green cover, where
   ever the green index is low. This technique presents intra-city green
   cover pattern analysis. Such analysis emphasises to reserve the space
